title: Shannon Egoiste | OC Ref
description:
__Shannon Egoiste__
Their gender expression are either androginous or masculine, with huge fashion preference toward Visual Kei,cyber/warcore fashion (but can wear absolutely everything nonetheless), Often have a scarf/piece of fabric with Tartan pattern tied to their belt. They wear glasses but don't really need them ! **Always** have their Hair Tied with a high ponytails.
